@startuml 11-workflow-adlc

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Sans-Serif"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12

skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor #F4F4F4
  BorderColor #616161
  FontColor #212121
  ArrowColor #616161
  DiamondBackgroundColor #F4F4F4
  DiamondBorderColor #616161
}

skinparam activityDiagram {
  BackgroundColor white
}

|ADLC Workflow|

start
:""Raw idea"";

#E3F2FD:**1. SPECIFICATIONS (PRD)**
"What should the system do?"
Functional and non-functional requirements;

#E8F5E9:**2. USE CASES**
"How will users use it?"
Scenarios with actor, action, outcome;

#FFF3E0:**3. DESIGN**
"What architecture and technologies?"
AI proposes options, the human decides;

#F3E8FF:**4. EPICS**
"What work blocks are needed?"
Logical groupings (auth, CRUD, deploy...);

#FEF9C3:**5. TASKS**
"What atomic steps for each epic?"
Implementable units with Acceptance Criteria;

#FFEBEE:**6. IMPLEMENT**
"Execute the task and verify"
Code + tests + checkpoint;

stop

@enduml
